<c.Japanese>彼の死に際に放ったひと言は
人々を海へ駆り立てた</c.Japanese>

00:00:27.303--> 00:00:31.016 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゴールド･ロジャー）
<c.Japanese>俺の財宝か？</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>欲しけりゃくれてやる</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:00:31.141--> 00:00:34.644 position:80%
<c.Japanese>探せ！ この世のすべてを
そこに置いてきた</c.Japanese>

00:00:37.272--> 00:00:39.774 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ナレーション）
<c.Japanese>男たちは</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>グランドラインを目指し</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:00:39.899--> 00:00:41.651 position:80%
<c.Japanese>夢を追い続ける</c.Japanese>

00:00:42.027--> 00:00:45.071 position:80%
<c.Japanese>世は まさに大海賊時代！</c.Japanese>

00:00:45.989--> 00:00:51.995 position:80%
<c.Japanese>♪～</c.Japanese>

00:01:58.978--> 00:02:05.485 position:80%
<c.Japanese>～♪</c.Japanese>

00:02:08.154--> 00:02:11.449 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
ウッホーッ いい天気だな</c.Japanese>

00:02:11.574--> 00:02:15.453 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
このまま進めば もうすぐ
海軍基地の島が見えてきますよ</c.Japanese>

00:02:15.662--> 00:02:19.916 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
へーっ コビー お前 すごいな
ちゃんと目的地に着くのか？</c.Japanese>

00:02:20.041--> 00:02:23.545 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
当たり前です　海に出る者の
最低限の能力です</c.Japanese>

00:02:23.670--> 00:02:25.797 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）ハッハッハッハ…</c.Japanese>

00:02:25.922--> 00:02:28.967 position:80%
<c.Japanese>笑ってる場合じゃありませんよ
ルフィさん</c.Japanese>

00:02:29.092--> 00:02:30.885 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そこに捕まってるんです</c.Japanese>

00:02:31.427--> 00:02:33.847 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あの有名な海賊狩り</c.Japanese>

00:02:34.764--> 00:02:36.558 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ロロノア･ゾロが</c.Japanese>

00:02:37.267--> 00:02:38.226 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（刀で斬る音）</c.Japanese>

00:02:40.228--> 00:02:43.982 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
<c.Japanese>血に飢えた獣のように</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>賞金首を襲い</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:02:44.107--> 00:02:46.359 position:80%
<c.Japanese>切り刻んできた男</c.Japanese>

00:02:47.443--> 00:02:51.114 position:80%
<c.Japanese>人間の姿をした魔獣だと
人は言います</c.Japanese>

00:02:54.993--> 00:02:59.414 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
<c.Japanese>「大剣豪 現る！</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>海賊狩りロロノア･ゾロ」</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:03:06.129--> 00:03:07.380 position:80%
<c.Japanese>着いたーっ</c.Japanese>

00:03:07.797--> 00:03:09.799 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海軍基地の町</c.Japanese>

00:03:14.262--> 00:03:15.513 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ねえ ルフィさん</c.Japanese>

00:03:15.638--> 00:03:18.600 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あんなやつを仲間にしようだなんて
ムチャですよ</c.Japanese>

00:03:18.725--> 00:03:21.561 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
まだ決めたわけじゃないさ
もし いいやつだったら</c.Japanese>

00:03:21.686--> 00:03:23.938 position:80%
<c.Japanese>悪いやつだから
捕まってるんです</c.Japanese>

00:03:25.940--> 00:03:28.776 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
あっ うん うん うまい</c.Japanese>

00:03:29.402--> 00:03:32.155 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あの基地にいるのかな？
ゾロってやつ</c.Japanese>

00:03:32.280--> 00:03:33.865 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（町の人たちの驚く声）</c.Japanese>

00:03:37.744--> 00:03:40.330 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ここでゾロの名は
禁句のようですね</c.Japanese>

00:03:41.289--> 00:03:42.832 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
とにかく基地に行ってみよう</c.Japanese>

00:03:42.957--> 00:03:44.626 position:80%
<c.Japanese>お前 海兵になるんだろ？</c.Japanese>

00:03:44.751--> 00:03:48.087 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
え？ ええ でも まだ心の準備が</c.Japanese>

00:03:48.212--> 00:03:52.258 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うわさでは この基地に
モーガン大佐って人がいるとか…</c.Japanese>

00:03:52.383--> 00:03:53.801 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（町の人たちの驚く声）</c.Japanese>

00:03:57.555--> 00:04:00.725 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ハハハハハッ <c.Japanese>面白</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>おもしれ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>え町だな</c.Japanese>

00:04:00.850--> 00:04:03.311 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
妙ですよ ゾロはともかく<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:04:03.436--> 00:04:05.897 position:80%
<c.Japanese>なぜ海軍大佐の名にまで
おびえるんでしょうか？</c.Japanese>

00:04:06.981--> 00:04:09.859 position:80%
<c.Japanese>僕 何だか不安になってきました</c.Japanese>

00:04:09.984--> 00:04:12.320 position:80%
<c.Japanese>なんかノリで
吹っ飛んじゃったんじゃねえか？</c.Japanese>

00:04:12.445--> 00:04:13.905 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そんなわけないでしょう</c.Japanese>

00:04:15.949--> 00:04:17.325 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）おっし ここだな</c.Japanese>

00:04:18.368--> 00:04:20.745 position:80%
<c.Japanese>とうとう来たんだ</c.Japanese>

00:04:21.454--> 00:04:26.084 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ここでお別れですね ルフィさん
短い間でしたが… うん？</c.Japanese>

00:04:26.376--> 00:04:27.377 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）よっこらせっと</c.Japanese>

00:04:27.502--> 00:04:29.671 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
ああっ ルフィさん
いきなり なんてことを</c.Japanese>

00:04:30.088--> 00:04:32.382 position:80%
<c.Japanese>どこだ？ 魔獣は</c.Japanese>

00:04:32.715--> 00:04:34.717 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
こんなとこにいませんよ</c.Japanese>

00:04:34.842--> 00:04:36.886 position:80%
<c.Japanese>きっと奥の独房とか…</c.Japanese>

00:04:37.011--> 00:04:37.929 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）いた！</c.Japanese>

00:04:38.054--> 00:04:39.180 position:80%
<c.Japanese>それーい</c.Japanese>

00:04:42.058--> 00:04:42.892 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ほら あいつ</c.Japanese>

00:04:43.017--> 00:04:45.144 position:80%
<c.Japanese>もう いるわけないですよ</c.Japanese>

00:04:45.270--> 00:04:46.271 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ううっ！</c.Japanese>

00:04:51.067--> 00:04:54.570 position:80%
<c.Japanese>黒頭巾に腹巻き…</c.Japanese>

00:04:56.239--> 00:04:59.450 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あれがロロノア･ゾロ</c.Japanese>

00:04:59.575--> 00:05:01.995 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あの縄ほどけば
簡単に逃がせるな</c.Japanese>

00:05:02.120--> 00:05:04.205 position:80%
<c.Japanese>バ… バカなこと
言わないでください</c.Japanese>

00:05:04.330--> 00:05:05.999 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あんなやつ 逃がしたら
どうなるか</c.Japanese>

00:05:06.457--> 00:05:09.168 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ルフィさんだって
殺そうとしますよ きっと</c.Japanese>

00:05:09.294--> 00:05:11.170 position:80%
<c.Japanese>大丈夫　俺 強いから</c.Japanese>

00:05:11.421--> 00:05:13.673 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）<c.Japanese>もう この人は！</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:05:14.257--> 00:05:15.967 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）おい お前ら</c.Japanese>

00:05:17.385--> 00:05:18.761 position:80%
<c.Japanese>目障りだ</c.Japanese>

00:05:21.180--> 00:05:22.181 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うせろ</c.Japanese>

00:05:22.307--> 00:05:23.391 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）ヒャーッ</c.Japanese>

00:05:23.516--> 00:05:24.225 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ルフィさん</c.Japanese>

00:05:24.350--> 00:05:27.061 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あんなやつ 仲間にしたら
命がいくつあっても…</c.Japanese>

00:05:27.186--> 00:05:27.854 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うん？</c.Japanese>

00:05:29.689--> 00:05:31.065 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカ）シーッ</c.Japanese>

00:05:37.530--> 00:05:38.781 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）わあ 危ない</c.Japanese>

00:05:38.906--> 00:05:42.035 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ルフィさん 止めてください
あの子 殺されちゃいますよ</c.Japanese>

00:05:43.411--> 00:05:44.329 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）何だ？</c.Japanese>

00:05:44.454--> 00:05:45.955 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おなかすいたでしょ？</c.Japanese>

00:05:46.080--> 00:05:48.124 position:80%
<c.Japanese>私 おにぎり作ってきたの</c.Japanese>

00:05:48.249--> 00:05:50.793 position:80%
<c.Japanese>殺されてえのか チビ
消えな</c.Japanese>

00:05:50.918--> 00:05:53.379 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカ）
お兄ちゃん もうずっと
何も食べてないんでしょ？</c.Japanese>

00:05:53.963--> 00:05:54.756 position:80%
<c.Japanese>はい</c.Japanese>

00:05:54.922--> 00:05:59.260 position:80%
<c.Japanese>私 初めてだけど
一生懸命 作ったから</c.Japanese>

00:06:01.095--> 00:06:02.805 position:80%
<c.Japanese>腹なんか減っちゃいねえ</c.Japanese>

00:06:02.930--> 00:06:04.390 position:80%
<c.Japanese>目障りだ　とっとと帰れ</c.Japanese>

00:06:04.515--> 00:06:05.141 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカ）でも…</c.Japanese>

00:06:05.266--> 00:06:07.560 position:80%
<c.Japanese>要らねえっつったろ
ぶっ飛ばすぞ</c.Japanese>

00:06:08.269--> 00:06:10.354 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）
いじめは いかんねえ</c.Japanese>

00:06:11.898--> 00:06:17.195 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘヘヘッ… 意外と元気じゃないか
ロロノア･ゾロ</c.Japanese>

00:06:17.612--> 00:06:19.655 position:80%
<c.Japanese>また変なのが出てきたなあ</c.Japanese>

00:06:19.781--> 00:06:22.492 position:80%
<c.Japanese>よかったあ
きっと海軍の人ですよ</c.Japanese>

00:06:22.617--> 00:06:24.077 position:80%
<c.Japanese>これであの子 大丈夫です</c.Japanese>

00:06:24.827--> 00:06:27.497 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おや？ おいしそうな
おにぎりだねえ</c.Japanese>

00:06:27.622--> 00:06:29.207 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ふっ！
（リカ）ダメッ</c.Japanese>

00:06:30.208--> 00:06:32.502 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）
ん？ あーっ クソ<c.Japanese>甘</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>あめ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>え</c.Japanese>

00:06:32.627--> 00:06:34.378 position:80%
<c.Japanese>砂糖だらけじゃねえか</c.Japanese>

00:06:34.504--> 00:06:36.506 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おにぎりは普通 塩だろうが 塩</c.Japanese>

00:06:36.839--> 00:06:39.675 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だって…
甘いほうがおいしいと思って</c.Japanese>

00:06:39.801--> 00:06:41.636 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）
この！ こんな物 こんな物</c.Japanese>

00:06:41.761--> 00:06:43.805 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカ）やめて やめてーっ</c.Japanese>

00:06:43.930--> 00:06:45.056 position:80%
<c.Japanese>なんてひどいことを…</c.Japanese>

00:06:47.183--> 00:06:49.185 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカ）ああ…</c.Japanese>

00:06:50.144--> 00:06:55.233 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うう… 私
一生懸命 作ったのに…</c.Japanese>

00:06:55.566--> 00:06:59.153 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あ～あ お前 この貼り紙
読まなかったのか？</c.Japanese>

00:06:59.779--> 00:07:03.074 position:80%
<c.Japanese>“罪人に肩入れし者 死刑に処す”</c.Japanese>

00:07:03.199--> 00:07:04.867 position:80%
<c.Japanese>“海軍大佐 モーガン”</c.Japanese>

00:07:04.992--> 00:07:05.910 position:80%
<c.Japanese>えっ？</c.Japanese>

00:07:06.119--> 00:07:07.495 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘッヘヘへ…</c.Japanese>

00:07:07.620--> 00:07:10.540 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ガキでも<c.Japanese>親父</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>おやじ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>の怖さは
知ってるようだな</c.Japanese>

00:07:11.082--> 00:07:12.166 position:80%
<c.Japanese>親父？</c.Japanese>

00:07:12.291--> 00:07:14.836 position:80%
<c.Japanese>じゃあ あれは
モーガン大佐の息子？</c.Japanese>

00:07:15.378--> 00:07:17.296 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おい このガキ 投げ捨てろ</c.Japanese>

00:07:17.421--> 00:07:18.089 position:80%
<c.Japanese>は？</c.Japanese>

00:07:18.297--> 00:07:19.340 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あ… あ…</c.Japanese>

00:07:19.465--> 00:07:21.926 position:80%
<c.Japanese>塀の外へ
投げ飛ばせっつったんだよ</c.Japanese>

00:07:22.051--> 00:07:25.388 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺の命令が聞けないのか？
親父に言いつけるぞ</c.Japanese>

00:07:25.513--> 00:07:26.889 position:80%
<c.Japanese>はい ただ今</c.Japanese>

00:07:27.181--> 00:07:28.558 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あ…</c.Japanese>

00:07:28.933--> 00:07:30.059 position:80%
<c.Japanese>イヤッ</c.Japanese>

00:07:30.184--> 00:07:33.020 position:80%
<c.Japanese>すまん 嬢ちゃん 体を丸めて</c.Japanese>

00:07:33.146--> 00:07:33.855 position:80%
<c.Japanese>え？</c.Japanese>

00:07:34.105--> 00:07:34.856 position:80%
<c.Japanese>キャーッ</c.Japanese>

00:07:35.565--> 00:07:37.483 position:80%
<c.Japanese>キャーッ</c.Japanese>

00:07:41.821--> 00:07:43.531 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あっ ありがとう</c.Japanese>

00:07:43.656--> 00:07:45.700 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
大丈夫ですか？ ルフィさん</c.Japanese>

00:07:46.075--> 00:07:47.743 position:80%
<c.Japanese>君 ケガはないかい？</c.Japanese>

00:07:47.869--> 00:07:50.204 position:80%
<c.Japanese>しかし なんてひどいやつなんだ</c.Japanese>

00:07:50.329--> 00:07:51.914 position:80%
<c.Japanese>どこも痛くないかい？</c.Japanese>

00:07:52.457--> 00:07:53.332 position:80%
<c.Japanese>貴様</c.Japanese>

00:07:53.458--> 00:07:57.628 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘヘヘへッ ヘヘヘヘッ…</c.Japanese>

00:07:57.753--> 00:08:01.174 position:80%
<c.Japanese>しかし しぶとく生きてやがるな
てめえは</c.Japanese>

00:08:01.299--> 00:08:04.469 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ああ ちゃんと１か月
生き延びてやるさ</c.Japanese>

00:08:04.594--> 00:08:06.304 position:80%
<c.Japanese>まっ せいぜい頑張ってね</c.Japanese>

00:08:06.429--> 00:08:09.557 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘヘヘヘッ ヘヘヘヘッ…</c.Japanese>

00:08:09.682--> 00:08:11.392 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あと10日だからな</c.Japanese>

00:08:11.517--> 00:08:15.438 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）
それまで生きていられたらねえ
ヘヘヘヘッ…</c.Japanese>

00:08:16.105--> 00:08:19.317 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
なんてひどいこと
するんでしょうねえ ルフィさん</c.Japanese>

00:08:19.692--> 00:08:21.486 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ん？ いない～！？</c.Japanese>

00:08:22.570--> 00:08:23.613 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ん？</c.Japanese>

00:08:23.946--> 00:08:25.990 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
お前 悪いやつなんだってな</c.Japanese>

00:08:26.115--> 00:08:27.658 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）
てめえ まだいたのか</c.Japanese>

00:08:27.783--> 00:08:31.704 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
こんなとこで さらしもんになって
お前 ホントに強いのか？</c.Japanese>

00:08:31.829--> 00:08:33.080 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）余計なお世話だ</c.Japanese>

00:08:33.206--> 00:08:34.665 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）ふーん</c.Japanese>

00:08:36.501--> 00:08:39.086 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺だったら
３日で餓死するな きっと</c.Japanese>

00:08:39.212--> 00:08:41.547 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）
お前とじゃ気力が違うんだ</c.Japanese>

00:08:42.715--> 00:08:45.092 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺は必ず生き延びてみせる</c.Japanese>

00:08:45.843--> 00:08:47.178 position:80%
<c.Japanese>絶対に</c.Japanese>

00:08:47.720--> 00:08:49.847 position:80%
<c.Japanese>へえ～ 物好きなやつ</c.Japanese>

00:08:49.972--> 00:08:50.973 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ちょっと待て
（ルフィ）あん？</c.Japanese>

00:08:52.350--> 00:08:54.227 position:80%
<c.Japanese>それ 取ってくんねえか</c.Japanese>

00:08:55.853--> 00:08:57.688 position:80%
<c.Japanese>食うのかよ これ</c.Japanese>

00:08:57.939--> 00:08:59.607 position:80%
<c.Japanese>もう ほとんど泥の塊だぞ</c.Japanese>

00:08:59.857--> 00:09:01.234 position:80%
<c.Japanese>黙って食わせろ</c.Japanese>

00:09:01.817--> 00:09:02.652 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あ？</c.Japanese>

00:09:06.405--> 00:09:07.782 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロのせき込み）</c.Japanese>

00:09:07.907--> 00:09:09.325 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だから言ったろ</c.Japanese>

00:09:09.450--> 00:09:10.826 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）うまかった</c.Japanese>

00:09:12.119--> 00:09:13.329 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ごちそうさま</c.Japanese>

00:09:15.790--> 00:09:17.124 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカ）ホント？</c.Japanese>

00:09:17.833--> 00:09:21.212 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ああ １つ残らず
食っちまったよ あいつ</c.Japanese>

00:09:21.379--> 00:09:22.547 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うれしい</c.Japanese>

00:09:22.672--> 00:09:26.133 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ゾロってホントに
うわさほどの悪人なんでしょうか</c.Japanese>

00:09:26.384--> 00:09:28.010 position:80%
<c.Japanese>違うよ</c.Japanese>

00:09:28.261--> 00:09:32.682 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だって お兄ちゃん
私たちの代わりに<c.Japanese>磔</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>はりつけ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>に…</c.Japanese>

00:09:32.807--> 00:09:34.976 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あ？ どういうことだ？</c.Japanese>

00:09:35.309--> 00:09:37.770 position:80%
<c.Japanese>みんな
あのヘルメッポのせいなの</c.Japanese>

00:09:39.105--> 00:09:41.524 position:80%
<c.Japanese>モーガン大佐の息子の…</c.Japanese>

00:09:43.025--> 00:09:44.652 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）どけ どけーっ</c.Japanese>

00:09:44.777--> 00:09:48.614 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺のかわいいペット様に
道を空けろ</c.Japanese>

00:09:48.739--> 00:09:51.450 position:80%
<c.Japanese>邪魔するやつは死刑だぞ</c.Japanese>

00:09:53.369--> 00:09:54.036 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ハッ！</c.Japanese>

00:09:57.999--> 00:09:59.375 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ダメ やめて</c.Japanese>

00:09:59.709--> 00:10:00.960 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おい お前</c.Japanese>

00:10:01.085--> 00:10:04.088 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺のペット様のやることに
文句つける気か？</c.Japanese>

00:10:04.380--> 00:10:07.300 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカの母）
リカ やめなさい
逆らったら大変なことに</c.Japanese>

00:10:07.550--> 00:10:10.511 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘッヘヘへ ヘヘヘッ…</c.Japanese>

00:10:10.678--> 00:10:11.470 position:80%
<c.Japanese>キャーッ！</c.Japanese>

00:10:12.430--> 00:10:13.389 position:80%
<c.Japanese>どわあ</c.Japanese>

00:10:13.598--> 00:10:15.641 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（男性Ａ）
はあ… やりやがった</c.Japanese>

00:10:15.766--> 00:10:17.476 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（男性Ｂ）
ただじゃ済まねえぞ</c.Japanese>

00:10:18.936--> 00:10:20.396 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何だ 貴様は</c.Japanese>

00:10:20.521--> 00:10:22.273 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ええ？ お前はまさか…</c.Japanese>

00:10:23.274--> 00:10:25.151 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海賊狩りのゾロか？</c.Japanese>

00:10:25.276--> 00:10:26.944 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）だったら何だ？</c.Japanese>

00:10:27.069--> 00:10:29.947 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海賊狩りが
なんで海軍に盾突くんだ</c.Japanese>

00:10:30.072--> 00:10:32.199 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）
メシくらい静かに食わせろ</c.Japanese>

00:10:33.284--> 00:10:34.035 position:80%
<c.Japanese>この！</c.Japanese>

00:10:34.577--> 00:10:35.494 position:80%
<c.Japanese>どわあ</c.Japanese>

00:10:35.953--> 00:10:37.997 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うわあ ぐおっ</c.Japanese>

00:10:42.460--> 00:10:43.294 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うう…</c.Japanese>

00:10:43.461--> 00:10:44.128 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヒャーッ</c.Japanese>

00:10:45.212--> 00:10:50.926 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）
うるせえんだよ
おめえも おめえのペット様もよ</c.Japanese>

00:10:51.344--> 00:10:53.346 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うう…</c.Japanese>

00:10:53.471--> 00:10:54.347 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うっ</c.Japanese>

00:10:54.472--> 00:10:57.224 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘヘヘッ 分かってるのか？</c.Japanese>

00:10:57.350--> 00:10:59.477 position:80%
<c.Japanese>このことが親父に知れれば<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:10:59.935--> 00:11:02.355 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そいつらは間違いなく死刑だぞ</c.Japanese>

00:11:04.065--> 00:11:05.316 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘヘッ…</c.Japanese>

00:11:05.441--> 00:11:08.402 position:80%
<c.Japanese>どうだ 取引しようじゃねえか</c.Japanese>

00:11:08.527--> 00:11:12.323 position:80%
<c.Japanese>こいつら親子の代わりに
お前が磔になれ</c.Japanese>

00:11:12.657--> 00:11:14.784 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そうだな １か月</c.Japanese>

00:11:14.909--> 00:11:20.039 position:80%
<c.Japanese>１か月 生き延びりゃ
お前の命も見逃してやるぜ</c.Japanese>

00:11:20.164--> 00:11:21.666 position:80%
<c.Japanese>どうする？</c.Japanese>

00:11:23.292--> 00:11:24.794 position:80%
<c.Japanese>１か月だな？</c.Japanese>

00:11:27.880--> 00:11:29.840 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（リカ）
<c.Japanese>あれから３週間</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:11:31.842--> 00:11:33.219 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘルメッポのやつ</c.Japanese>

00:11:33.386--> 00:11:36.764 position:80%
<c.Japanese>磔にしたお兄ちゃんを
殴ったり蹴ったり…</c.Japanese>

00:11:36.889--> 00:11:39.517 position:80%
<c.Japanese>私… 私…</c.Japanese>

00:11:39.642--> 00:11:41.268 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そうだったんですか</c.Japanese>

00:11:41.394--> 00:11:42.645 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ガラスが割れる音）</c.Japanese>

00:11:42.895--> 00:11:43.521 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）だあ？</c.Japanese>

00:11:44.271--> 00:11:47.858 position:80%
<c.Japanese>腹減った
俺たち全員にタダで食わせろ</c.Japanese>

00:11:47.983--> 00:11:51.612 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘッヘヘヘヘ
おい 早く酒 持ってこい</c.Japanese>

00:11:51.737--> 00:11:55.783 position:80%
<c.Japanese>モタモタしてんじゃねえぞ おら
早くしろ</c.Japanese>

00:11:55.908--> 00:11:57.076 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘヘヘヘッ</c.Japanese>

00:11:57.201--> 00:12:00.246 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ああ そうそう
ここんところ退屈だから<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:12:00.371--> 00:12:02.415 position:80%
<c.Japanese>明日 ゾロを
処刑することにしたぞ</c.Japanese>

00:12:02.957--> 00:12:04.625 position:80%
<c.Japanese>みんな 楽しみに待ってろ</c.Japanese>

00:12:04.750--> 00:12:07.503 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘヘヘヘヘッ…</c.Japanese>

00:12:09.505--> 00:12:10.506 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）ううっ</c.Japanese>

00:12:14.218--> 00:12:15.845 position:80%
<c.Japanese>なっ 何だよ お前は？</c.Japanese>

00:12:15.970--> 00:12:17.930 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
ルフィさん やめてください</c.Japanese>

00:12:18.055--> 00:12:19.390 position:80%
<c.Japanese>こいつ クズだ</c.Japanese>

00:12:19.515--> 00:12:23.936 position:80%
<c.Japanese>なっ 殴りやがったな
俺はモーガン大佐の息子だぞ</c.Japanese>

00:12:24.061--> 00:12:25.062 position:80%
<c.Japanese>それがどうした</c.Japanese>

00:12:25.563--> 00:12:28.023 position:80%
<c.Japanese>親父に言いつけて
死刑にしてやる</c.Japanese>

00:12:28.524--> 00:12:30.234 position:80%
<c.Japanese>お前がかかってこいよ</c.Japanese>

00:12:30.359--> 00:12:31.944 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ルフィさん 落ち着いて</c.Japanese>

00:12:32.069--> 00:12:34.113 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海軍を敵に回す気ですか</c.Japanese>

00:12:34.238--> 00:12:35.906 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）決めたぞ コビー</c.Japanese>

00:12:37.241--> 00:12:38.200 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺は…</c.Japanese>

00:12:38.909--> 00:12:40.828 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ゾロを仲間にする！</c.Japanese>

00:12:45.416--> 00:12:48.544 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）俺は… 偉い！</c.Japanese>

00:12:48.878--> 00:12:51.839 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵）
はっ！ そのとおりであります
モーガン大佐</c.Japanese>

00:12:51.964--> 00:12:55.885 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
その割には近頃
“貢ぎ”が少ねえんじゃねえか？</c.Japanese>

00:12:56.135--> 00:13:00.681 position:80%
<c.Japanese>は… なにぶん 町の者たちの
懐にも限界がありまして</c.Japanese>

00:13:01.724--> 00:13:04.602 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
問題は俺への敬服度</c.Japanese>

00:13:05.269--> 00:13:06.896 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そうじゃねえか？</c.Japanese>

00:13:07.021--> 00:13:07.855 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポの荒い息）</c.Japanese>

00:13:08.814--> 00:13:10.107 position:80%
<c.Japanese>親父</c.Japanese>

00:13:10.524--> 00:13:14.403 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ぶち殺してほしいやつが
いるんだよ</c.Japanese>

00:13:37.218--> 00:13:41.180 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（竹刀で打ち合う音）</c.Japanese>

00:13:44.141--> 00:13:45.643 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（くいな）やあ
（ゾロ）だあ</c.Japanese>

00:13:48.229--> 00:13:50.606 position:80%
<c.Japanese>相変わらず弱いわね ゾロ</c.Japanese>

00:13:52.650--> 00:13:54.109 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）<c.Japanese>約束したんだ</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:13:55.361--> 00:13:58.906 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺は こんなところで
死ぬわけにはいかねえんだ</c.Japanese>

00:14:03.869--> 00:14:04.745 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ハッ！</c.Japanese>

00:14:08.791--> 00:14:09.625 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ん？</c.Japanese>

00:14:10.209--> 00:14:13.128 position:80%
<c.Japanese>またおめえか？ 暇なやつだ</c.Japanese>

00:14:13.254--> 00:14:15.714 position:80%
<c.Japanese>縄 解いてやるから
俺の仲間になってくれ</c.Japanese>

00:14:15.839--> 00:14:16.840 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何だと？</c.Japanese>

00:14:16.966--> 00:14:20.177 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺は一緒に海賊になる
仲間を探してるんだ</c.Japanese>

00:14:20.469--> 00:14:23.931 position:80%
<c.Japanese>断る　自分から悪党に
成り下がろうってのか？</c.Japanese>

00:14:24.056--> 00:14:25.641 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ご苦労なこって</c.Japanese>

00:14:25.766--> 00:14:27.601 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海賊のどこが悪い</c.Japanese>

00:14:27.726--> 00:14:30.062 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海賊なんて外道だ
誰がなるか</c.Japanese>

00:14:30.187--> 00:14:31.689 position:80%
<c.Japanese>別にいいじゃんか</c.Japanese>

00:14:31.814--> 00:14:35.109 position:80%
<c.Japanese>もともとお前 悪い賞金稼ぎって
言われてるんだから</c.Japanese>

00:14:35.776--> 00:14:38.237 position:80%
<c.Japanese>世間がどう言おうと勝手だが<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:14:38.362--> 00:14:40.573 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺は後悔するようなことは
やっちゃいねえ</c.Japanese>

00:14:41.574--> 00:14:43.826 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何が何でも生き延びて<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:14:44.285--> 00:14:46.537 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺は俺のやりたいことを
成し遂げる</c.Japanese>

00:14:46.954--> 00:14:48.664 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ああ？ そっか</c.Japanese>

00:14:49.248--> 00:14:51.709 position:80%
<c.Japanese>でも俺は お前を
仲間にするって決めた</c.Japanese>

00:14:51.834--> 00:14:53.335 position:80%
<c.Japanese>勝手に決めんな</c.Japanese>

00:14:53.460--> 00:14:54.962 position:80%
<c.Japanese>お前 刀使うんだってな</c.Japanese>

00:14:55.462--> 00:14:59.300 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）
ああ だがあのバカ息子が
持ってっちまったよ</c.Japanese>

00:14:59.592--> 00:15:00.843 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺が取り返してくるよ</c.Japanese>

00:15:00.968--> 00:15:01.844 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）何？</c.Japanese>

00:15:01.969--> 00:15:04.805 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だから 刀が欲しけりゃ
俺の仲間になれ</c.Japanese>

00:15:04.930--> 00:15:06.181 position:80%
<c.Japanese>たち<c.Japanese>悪</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>わり</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>いぞ てめえ</c.Japanese>

00:15:06.599--> 00:15:07.349 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）ハハハハッ</c.Japanese>

00:15:08.142--> 00:15:10.895 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あいつ １人で基地に
乗り込むつもりか？</c.Japanese>

00:15:11.020--> 00:15:11.687 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あっ…</c.Japanese>

00:15:12.187--> 00:15:14.440 position:80%
<c.Japanese>バカ 基地は反対だ
そっちじゃねえ</c.Japanese>

00:15:15.232--> 00:15:16.066 position:80%
<c.Japanese>え？</c.Japanese>

00:15:17.276--> 00:15:19.695 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ゴムゴムの ロケット！</c.Japanese>

00:15:20.446--> 00:15:24.199 position:80%
<c.Japanese>なっ あいつ…
一体 何者なんだ？</c.Japanese>

00:15:25.618--> 00:15:30.122 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）
わっせ わっせ わっせ…</c.Japanese>

00:15:30.873--> 00:15:34.126 position:80%
<c.Japanese>わっせ わっせ…</c.Japanese>

00:15:34.251--> 00:15:36.420 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
よーし そこで止めろ</c.Japanese>

00:15:37.004--> 00:15:38.797 position:80%
<c.Japanese>一気に立たせるんだ</c.Japanese>

00:15:40.049--> 00:15:42.551 position:80%
<c.Japanese>親父 なんで仕返しに
行かねえんだ</c.Japanese>

00:15:42.676--> 00:15:44.386 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺を殴ったやつだぜ</c.Japanese>

00:15:44.511--> 00:15:48.265 position:80%
<c.Japanese>親父にも殴られたことのない
この俺の顔を</c.Japanese>

00:15:48.390--> 00:15:52.269 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
今まで なぜ俺が
お前を殴らなかったか<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:15:53.062--> 00:15:53.938 position:80%
<c.Japanese>分かるか</c.Japanese>

00:15:54.063--> 00:15:54.980 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ええ？</c.Japanese>

00:15:55.105--> 00:15:56.732 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そりゃ親父にとって俺が…</c.Japanese>

00:15:57.524--> 00:15:58.609 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）そう…</c.Japanese>

00:15:59.360--> 00:16:00.945 position:80%
<c.Japanese>お前が…</c.Japanese>

00:16:01.946--> 00:16:03.072 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）ぶえっ</c.Japanese>

00:16:07.993--> 00:16:12.206 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
殴る価値もねえ
バカ息子だからよ</c.Japanese>

00:16:12.957--> 00:16:14.041 position:80%
<c.Japanese>勘違いするなよ</c.Japanese>

00:16:14.166--> 00:16:17.962 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）うわああ…</c.Japanese>

00:16:18.087--> 00:16:20.547 position:80%
<c.Japanese>偉いのは てめえの親父</c.Japanese>

00:16:20.673--> 00:16:22.299 position:80%
<c.Japanese>つまり この俺様だ</c.Japanese>

00:16:25.469--> 00:16:29.223 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そういや ネズミが１匹
磔場に侵入したらしいな</c.Japanese>

00:16:29.515--> 00:16:33.686 position:80%
<c.Japanese>え？ あ… あのチビなら
ちゃんと俺が痛めつけて…</c.Japanese>

00:16:33.811--> 00:16:35.229 position:80%
<c.Japanese>殺したんだろうな？</c.Japanese>

00:16:35.562--> 00:16:38.691 position:80%
<c.Japanese>え？ いや だってあれは
まだほんのガキだし</c.Japanese>

00:16:39.692--> 00:16:41.276 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）おい お前</c.Japanese>

00:16:41.402--> 00:16:42.861 position:80%
<c.Japanese>町へ行って始末してこい</c.Japanese>

00:16:43.570--> 00:16:46.240 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（中尉）
そんな… まだ幼い少女です</c.Japanese>

00:16:46.365--> 00:16:48.325 position:80%
<c.Japanese>いくら大佐の命令でも…</c.Japanese>

00:16:48.450--> 00:16:52.955 position:80%
<c.Japanese>たとえガキでも
俺の命令に背けば反逆者だ</c.Japanese>

00:16:53.080--> 00:16:55.457 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（中尉）
しかし… できません</c.Japanese>

00:16:55.749--> 00:16:57.334 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）んん？</c.Japanese>

00:16:57.751--> 00:16:59.086 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（中尉）うおおっ…</c.Japanese>

00:16:59.253--> 00:17:00.587 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うわーっ</c.Japanese>

00:17:00.713--> 00:17:01.922 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）中尉！</c.Japanese>

00:17:02.172--> 00:17:03.757 position:80%
<c.Japanese>なっ 何もそこまで…</c.Japanese>

00:17:04.717--> 00:17:08.887 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺は この腕っ節で
大佐にまで上りつめた</c.Japanese>

00:17:09.471--> 00:17:10.514 position:80%
<c.Japanese>いいか</c.Japanese>

00:17:10.639--> 00:17:12.599 position:80%
<c.Japanese>世の中 称号がすべてだ</c.Japanese>

00:17:13.642--> 00:17:17.271 position:80%
<c.Japanese>この基地で最高位の大佐である
この俺は<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:17:17.396--> 00:17:20.816 position:80%
<c.Japanese>最高に優れた人間である
ということだ</c.Japanese>

00:17:22.317--> 00:17:26.155 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だから俺のやることは
すべて正しい</c.Japanese>

00:17:26.780--> 00:17:28.157 position:80%
<c.Japanese>違うか てめえら！</c.Japanese>

00:17:28.615--> 00:17:30.242 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）
はっ！ そのとおりであります</c.Japanese>

00:17:30.909--> 00:17:33.120 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ガキの始末は後回しだ</c.Japanese>

00:17:33.662--> 00:17:37.041 position:80%
<c.Japanese>見ろ 長い年月をかけて
やっと完成した</c.Japanese>

00:17:37.624--> 00:17:40.127 position:80%
<c.Japanese>これが俺の権力の象徴だ</c.Japanese>

00:17:40.252--> 00:17:41.503 position:80%
<c.Japanese>さあ 像を起こせ</c.Japanese>

00:17:41.628--> 00:17:43.255 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）わっせ わっせ</c.Japanese>

00:17:43.380--> 00:17:46.717 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
この基地の頂点に
俺の偉大さを示すんだ</c.Japanese>

00:17:47.009--> 00:17:48.802 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）わっせ わっせ</c.Japanese>

00:17:50.345--> 00:17:52.765 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おっかしいな 誰もいねえや</c.Japanese>

00:17:52.890--> 00:17:56.101 position:80%
<c.Japanese>バカ息子を見つけて
ゾロの刀を取り戻さないとな</c.Japanese>

00:17:56.226--> 00:17:56.977 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あっ！</c.Japanese>

00:17:57.227--> 00:17:59.980 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）わっせ わっせ…
（モーガン）引け 引けーっ</c.Japanese>

00:18:00.230--> 00:18:02.941 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）
わっせ わっせ わっせ…</c.Japanese>

00:18:03.317--> 00:18:04.109 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵）うっ…</c.Japanese>

00:18:04.234--> 00:18:04.943 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うっ…</c.Japanese>

00:18:05.360--> 00:18:06.528 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）おい お前！</c.Japanese>

00:18:06.653--> 00:18:07.654 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヒャーッ</c.Japanese>

00:18:09.573--> 00:18:10.866 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ぶつけやがったな？</c.Japanese>

00:18:11.116--> 00:18:11.825 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）あん？</c.Japanese>

00:18:12.743--> 00:18:14.870 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何か上で音がしたな</c.Japanese>

00:18:15.913--> 00:18:18.874 position:80%
<c.Japanese>申し訳ありません
不注意でした！</c.Japanese>

00:18:18.999--> 00:18:22.878 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
この像は俺自身だと言ったはずだ</c.Japanese>

00:18:23.003--> 00:18:27.091 position:80%
<c.Japanese>傷１本 汚れ１つであれ
この俺への反逆だ</c.Japanese>

00:18:27.508--> 00:18:28.842 position:80%
<c.Japanese>行ってみようっと</c.Japanese>

00:18:29.384--> 00:18:31.428 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ゴムゴムのーっ</c.Japanese>

00:18:32.262--> 00:18:33.305 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ロケット！</c.Japanese>

00:18:33.430--> 00:18:34.348 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）思い知れい</c.Japanese>

00:18:35.015--> 00:18:35.933 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ほーっ！</c.Japanese>

00:18:36.058--> 00:18:37.434 position:80%
<c.Japanese>わあ 飛びすぎた</c.Japanese>

00:18:38.519--> 00:18:39.436 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何だ ありゃ</c.Japanese>

00:18:39.561--> 00:18:40.687 position:80%
<c.Japanese>下から飛んできた</c.Japanese>

00:18:41.522--> 00:18:43.398 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）止まった！
（海兵たち）おおっ…</c.Japanese>

00:18:43.565--> 00:18:44.983 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たち）ああーっ！</c.Japanese>

00:18:46.068--> 00:18:48.112 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵たちの踏ん張る声）</c.Japanese>

00:18:49.154--> 00:18:50.572 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（一同）ああ…</c.Japanese>

00:18:50.697--> 00:18:51.532 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あっ…</c.Japanese>

00:18:54.701--> 00:18:55.536 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ごめんなさい</c.Japanese>

00:18:58.664--> 00:19:01.208 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あいつを捕まえろ　俺が殺す</c.Japanese>

00:19:01.333--> 00:19:02.709 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（３人）はっ！ 大佐</c.Japanese>

00:19:02.960--> 00:19:05.379 position:80%
<c.Japanese>親父 こいつだ
俺を殴ったやつだ</c.Japanese>

00:19:05.504--> 00:19:06.213 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）あっ お前</c.Japanese>

00:19:06.880--> 00:19:07.798 position:80%
<c.Japanese>うああーっ</c.Japanese>

00:19:07.923--> 00:19:09.925 position:80%
<c.Japanese>捜してたんだ　一緒に来てくれ</c.Japanese>

00:19:10.050--> 00:19:11.510 position:80%
<c.Japanese>返してほしいもんがあるんだよ</c.Japanese>

00:19:11.844--> 00:19:13.887 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）はっ 放せ！
（海兵たち）ヘルメッポ様！</c.Japanese>

00:19:14.012--> 00:19:16.098 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）
追え！ 逃がすなーっ</c.Japanese>

00:19:16.223--> 00:19:18.559 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵）
大佐 磔場に誰かいます</c.Japanese>

00:19:18.684--> 00:19:20.018 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何？</c.Japanese>

00:19:24.731--> 00:19:27.985 position:80%
<c.Japanese>次から次に反逆者か…</c.Japanese>

00:19:31.446--> 00:19:33.115 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵Ａ）追え 追えーっ</c.Japanese>

00:19:33.448--> 00:19:35.200 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵Ｂ）早くしろーっ</c.Japanese>

00:19:37.828--> 00:19:39.580 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ナミ）
邪魔が入ったわね…</c.Japanese>

00:19:42.708--> 00:19:44.168 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ゾロの刀はどこだ？</c.Japanese>

00:19:44.501--> 00:19:46.003 position:80%
<c.Japanese>言う 言うから</c.Japanese>

00:19:46.128--> 00:19:48.630 position:80%
<c.Japanese>言うから 引きずるのやめてくれ</c.Japanese>

00:19:48.755--> 00:19:49.798 position:80%
<c.Japanese>よし 言え</c.Japanese>

00:19:49.923--> 00:19:52.885 position:80%
<c.Japanese>僕ちんの部屋にあります
さっき通り過ぎた…</c.Japanese>

00:19:53.010--> 00:19:54.720 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何だよ 早く言えよ</c.Japanese>

00:19:54.845--> 00:19:56.346 position:80%
<c.Japanese>戻んなきゃなんねえだろ</c.Japanese>

00:19:56.680--> 00:19:57.514 position:80%
<c.Japanese>動くな</c.Japanese>

00:19:57.639--> 00:19:59.099 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヘルメッポ様を放せ</c.Japanese>

00:19:59.725--> 00:20:00.767 position:80%
<c.Japanese>やだ</c.Japanese>

00:20:02.477--> 00:20:04.313 position:80%
<c.Japanese>撃てるもんなら撃ってみろ</c.Japanese>

00:20:04.605--> 00:20:06.481 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ヘルメッポ）
わーっ ダメ やめろーっ</c.Japanese>

00:20:06.815--> 00:20:08.192 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）それーっ</c.Japanese>

00:20:09.234--> 00:20:10.986 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
逃げてください ゾロさん</c.Japanese>

00:20:11.486--> 00:20:13.989 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そんなことすりゃ
お前 殺されるぞ</c.Japanese>

00:20:14.114--> 00:20:16.825 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
僕はもう
こんな海軍 見てられない</c.Japanese>

00:20:16.992--> 00:20:20.412 position:80%
<c.Japanese>僕は 正しい海兵に
なりたいんです</c.Japanese>

00:20:20.871--> 00:20:23.665 position:80%
<c.Japanese>やめろ
俺は逃げるわけにはいかねえんだ</c.Japanese>

00:20:23.790--> 00:20:24.625 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あと10日は…</c.Japanese>

00:20:24.750--> 00:20:26.835 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あなたは明日
処刑されるんですよ</c.Japanese>

00:20:26.960--> 00:20:27.711 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何？</c.Japanese>

00:20:28.295--> 00:20:32.758 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）
ヘルメッポは初めから あなたとの
約束を守る気なんてなかったんだ</c.Japanese>

00:20:32.966--> 00:20:37.054 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だから ルフィさんは怒って
ヘルメッポを殴ったんです</c.Japanese>

00:20:37.512--> 00:20:38.472 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あいつが…</c.Japanese>

00:20:38.680--> 00:20:42.059 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ルフィさんも
今は海軍に追われる身です</c.Japanese>

00:20:42.559--> 00:20:45.520 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あなたに海賊になれとまでは
言いません</c.Japanese>

00:20:45.812--> 00:20:46.939 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だけど お願いです</c.Japanese>

00:20:47.564--> 00:20:49.816 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ルフィさんに力を貸してください</c.Japanese>

00:20:53.737--> 00:20:57.491 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ゾロさんを助けられるのは
ルフィさんだけです</c.Japanese>

00:20:58.575--> 00:20:59.952 position:80%
<c.Japanese>そして今<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:21:00.077--> 00:21:04.873 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ルフィさんを助けられるのも
ゾロさんだけだと僕は思います</c.Japanese>

00:21:06.541--> 00:21:08.001 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）そこまでだ</c.Japanese>

00:21:10.754--> 00:21:12.673 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺様への反逆の罪で<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:21:12.798--> 00:21:15.676 position:80%
<c.Japanese>お前たち２人を
今 この場で処刑する</c.Japanese>

00:21:15.801--> 00:21:16.969 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（コビー）えーっ！</c.Japanese>

00:21:18.845--> 00:21:19.721 position:80%
<c.Japanese>この部屋だな</c.Japanese>

00:21:23.767--> 00:21:24.685 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あった！</c.Japanese>

00:21:25.894--> 00:21:27.854 position:80%
<c.Japanese>でも３本もあるぞ</c.Japanese>

00:21:27.980--> 00:21:29.606 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おい ゾロの刀はどれだ</c.Japanese>

00:21:30.607--> 00:21:32.401 position:80%
<c.Japanese>何だ 気絶してら</c.Japanese>

00:21:32.901--> 00:21:33.652 position:80%
<c.Japanese>お？</c.Japanese>

00:21:34.653--> 00:21:35.362 position:80%
<c.Japanese>コビー…</c.Japanese>

00:21:42.744--> 00:21:45.330 position:80%
<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>面白</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>おもしれ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>えことを
やってくれるじゃねえか<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:21:45.455--> 00:21:46.290 position:80%
<c.Japanese>おめえたち</c.Japanese>

00:21:47.291--> 00:21:51.336 position:80%
<c.Japanese>あの麦わら小僧と３人で
クーデターでも起こそうってのか</c.Japanese>

00:21:52.004--> 00:21:54.298 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）
俺はずっと１人で戦ってきた</c.Japanese>

00:21:55.007--> 00:21:58.719 position:80%
<c.Japanese>兵隊を取り巻きに威張り腐ってる
おめえとは違ってな</c.Japanese>

00:21:59.136--> 00:22:01.054 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）ロロノア･ゾロ</c.Japanese>

00:22:01.179--> 00:22:03.223 position:80%
<c.Japanese>この俺を甘く見るなよ</c.Japanese>

00:22:03.974--> 00:22:07.436 position:80%
<c.Japanese>貴様の強さなど
この俺の権力の前では<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:22:07.561--> 00:22:08.687 position:80%
<c.Japanese>カス同然だ</c.Japanese>

00:22:09.688--> 00:22:10.689 position:80%
<c.Japanese>構えろ</c.Japanese>

00:22:11.398--> 00:22:12.733 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）<c.Japanese>俺は…</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:22:15.777--> 00:22:18.822 position:80%
<c.Japanese>こんなところで
死ぬわけにはいかねえんだ</c.Japanese>

00:22:22.451--> 00:22:24.202 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（くいな）
相変わらず弱いのね ゾロ</c.Japanese>

00:22:26.705--> 00:22:28.957 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）ゴムゴムのーっ</c.Japanese>

00:22:29.082--> 00:22:30.125 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ロケット！</c.Japanese>

00:22:30.250--> 00:22:31.126 position:80%
<c.Japanese>撃て！</c.Japanese>

00:22:32.002--> 00:22:33.045 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）ぎゃあーっ</c.Japanese>

00:22:35.213--> 00:22:36.673 position:80%
<c.Japanese>お前！
（コビー）ルフィさん</c.Japanese>

00:22:36.798--> 00:22:38.258 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（モーガン）麦わら</c.Japanese>

00:22:38.925--> 00:22:40.677 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（海兵Ａ）うあーっ
（海兵Ｂ）ウソーッ</c.Japanese>

00:22:41.636--> 00:22:42.304 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヒヒッ</c.Japanese>

00:22:43.346--> 00:22:45.057 position:80%
<c.Japanese>効かーん！</c.Japanese>

00:22:46.933--> 00:22:49.644 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィの笑い声）</c.Japanese>

00:22:49.770--> 00:22:52.064 position:80%
<c.Japanese>だから言ったろ？
俺は強いって</c.Japanese>

00:22:52.397--> 00:22:55.275 position:80%
<c.Japanese>て… てめえ 一体何者だ？</c.Japanese>

00:22:56.485--> 00:22:58.487 position:80%
<c.Japanese>俺はモンキー･Ｄ･ルフィ</c.Japanese>

00:22:59.112--> 00:23:00.989 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海賊王になる男だ！</c.Japanese>

00:23:01.114--> 00:23:01.990 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ヒッ…</c.Japanese>

00:23:10.582--> 00:23:16.588 position:80%
<c.Japanese>♪～</c.Japanese>

00:24:14.062--> 00:24:20.068 position:80%
<c.Japanese>～♪</c.Japanese>

00:24:25.448--> 00:24:27.159 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）
<c.Japanese>俺は世界一の剣豪になるんだ</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:27.409--> 00:24:29.703 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
<c.Japanese>いいじゃん</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>大剣豪の海賊になれば</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:29.828--> 00:24:30.954 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）<c.Japanese>簡単に言うな</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:31.079--> 00:24:32.497 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ナミ）
<c.Japanese>兵士たちが騒ぎだしたわ</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:32.706--> 00:24:34.916 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
<c.Japanese>どうせ もう海軍</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>敵に回してんだから</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:35.041--> 00:24:36.626 position:80%
<c.Japanese>ほら 縄ほどいてやるよ</c.Japanese>

00:24:36.751--> 00:24:37.669 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ナミ）<c.Japanese>急がなきゃ</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:37.794--> 00:24:40.046 position:80%
<c.Japanese>グランドラインの海図は
この基地にあるはず</c.Japanese>

00:24:40.172--> 00:24:41.715 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
<c.Japanese>あれ？</c.Japanese>
<c.Japanese>もっと固くなっちゃった</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:41.840--> 00:24:42.757 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ゾロ）<c.Japanese>おい！</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:42.883--> 00:24:44.050 position:80%
<c.Japanese>（ルフィ）
<c.Japanese>次回 ワンピース</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

00:24:44.176--> 00:24:47.470 position:80%
<c.Japanese>「モーガン 対 ルフィ！
謎の美少女は誰？」</c.Japanese>

00:24:47.596--> 00:24:49.973 position:80%
<c.Japanese>海賊王に 俺はなる！</c.Japanese>